title: Howard Stern Shows AUG 2016
description:
Hey Nowwwwwwwwwwwwwwwwwwwwww!

It's nice to be back & able to share stuff with you guys & gals again. Though things are going to be a bit different this time around.

First off, I won't be posting shows early like I did before. I will leave that up to my buddy mc_gregor who is doing a great job. 
It will more likely be an end of that week post or when able.

As for Opie & Jim Norton, I may post the complete month of August, not sure yet. But if I do, after that it will be the same end of that week post or when able. 


I won't be posting The Artie Quitter Podcast for I canceled my sub just before August, for I'm about 4 months behind & saw no reason to keep paying, when I can sub again later once I've finished the episodes that I got & get a few month worth of shows then
